OL,6,FDetective Constable Victoria
OL,7,FHazlewood, who led the investigation,
OL,8,Fsaid: "McNamara is a serial fraudster,
OL,9,Fand I truly believe that he cannot
OL,10,Ftell the difference between reality
OL,11,Fand fantasy.
OL,13,F"During our investigation, we
OL,14,Funcovered a web of lies with thousands
OL,15,Fof text messages which he sent to his
OL,16,Fvictims in order to extort cash to
OL,17,Ffund his lavish lifestyle.
